{"tid":1816481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中東勢危】多間航空公司繞道不飛伊拉克伊朗上空 美FAA：避免被錯誤擊退","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T17:29:27.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8664bd06b8ba0ac6734c2b95dd8fda46b05decfe","tid":1816481,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"伊朗為報復將領蘇萊曼尼被殺，向伊拉克兩個有美軍駐紮的空軍基地發射逾10枚導彈。美國聯邦航空管理局（FAA）宣佈，考慮到緊張局勢下「有誤算或被錯誤識別的可能」，禁止民航機飛經伊拉克、伊朗、波斯灣及阿曼灣上空。全球多地包括台灣、新加坡、法國、加拿大、俄羅斯等都有航空公司改變航班航道，繞過伊朗空域以策安全，德國漢莎航空就暫時取消法蘭完福飛德克蘭的航線。國泰就表示已有一年沒有航班飛越伊拉克及伊朗上空，未來亦無計劃取經此航道。"},{"pid":"6cda756023ea1f54d13cc8375018d41623ca02fa","tid":1816481,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭墜機180人真心慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22421c3e183a0d3b54cece2c658a19494cc2f274","tid":1816481,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"一擊就擊落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擊退<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f06339228641365621035160d294e22727c2c7","tid":1816481,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"22421c3e183a0d3b54cece2c658a19494cc2f274","tid":1816481,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"一擊就擊落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擊退<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"以色列航空d機有裝防空導彈"},{"pid":"eb7016ff09e39c443668b4f8e99a1f2df6d0fc4d","tid":1816481,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cda756023ea1f54d13cc8375018d41623ca02fa","tid":1816481,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭墜機180人真心慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"